verbose_text: Indeed, a spontaneous destabilizing mutation in ESCRT-0 component Hrs, teetering (Hrs tn/tn), results in early-onset neuromuscular weakness and hypokinesis as observed in Plaa G23V / G23V mice, with accumulations of ubiquitylated synaptic proteins and disrupted SV recycling.
